{"tid":837387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐央行模擬貿戰 中國得益美重創","createTime":"2018-09-26T10:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T10:59:41.000Z","uid":10757,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d8e0f860d36c20002e0d41bc11c5c8d91ac311","tid":837387,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"歐洲央行公布一份模擬研究報告顯示，若美國與其他國家發動貿易戰，美國自身將嚴重受損，採取報復性措施的中國則處於良好的位置。<br />\n<br />\n歐央行模擬美國對所有進口商品加徵10%關稅，並且其他國家對其採取對等的報復行動。結果顯示，美國遭受貿易銳減、消費者和投資者信心下降的衝擊最大。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，美國的淨出口將會明顯惡化，當地企業將縮減投資及招聘，引發更大的負面影響。該行估計，美國的經濟增長將下降逾2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，中國則可望受惠於向第三國增加出口，但歐央行指，當中的益處可能被信心下降的負面影響所抵消。"},{"pid":"21999928d4ab5ec951ae2bd24cb7fb17f37ce6a5","tid":837387,"uid":91633,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"都要其他國家可以採取到對等的報復行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成篇廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0c3bdde9c77446b0c95ec31d0e8acc8fd3d5c6","tid":837387,"uid":31525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"中國或"},{"pid":"a0d8d1cdc866d0662f17fb3ecc89e4b4752d8b92","tid":837387,"uid":20414,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.cnn.com/2016/10/11/news/economy/trump-four-percent-growth-economists/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.cnn.com%2F2016%2F10%2F11%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Ftrump-four-percent-growth-economists%2Findex.html&d=1x%2BWbh8gi2e5EyRCu49XCBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=6c9316ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.cnn.com%2F2016%2F10%2F11%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Ftrump-four-percent-growth-economists%2Findex.html&h=24c2a8d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.cnn.com/2016/10/11/news/economy/trump-four-percent-growth-economists/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p